TITLE: Loading and Adding Video in Phaser 3
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to preload a video file and add it as a Video Game Object in a Phaser 3 game. The video is loaded in the preload function and then added to the game in the create function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.20/CHANGELOG-v3.20.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
preload () {
  this.load.video('pixar', 'nemo.mp4');
}

create () {
  this.add.video(400, 300, 'pixar');
}
```

