TITLE: Implementing ESM Imports with Phaser 3.60
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the new ESM support in Phaser 3.60 by importing specific modules and creating a basic game setup. Shows the modern ES Module import syntax and basic scene configuration with game initialization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.60/ESMSupport.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { AUTO, Scene, Game } from './phaser.esm.js';

class Test extends Scene
{
    constructor ()
    {
        super();
    }

    create ()
    {
        this.add.text(10, 10, 'Welcome to Phaser ESM');
    }
}

const config = {
    type: AUTO,
    width: 800,
    height: 600,
    parent: 'phaser-example',
    scene: [ Test ]
};

const game = new Game(config);
```

