TITLE: Installing Phaser Game CLI
DESCRIPTION: Commands to create new Phaser game projects using various package managers including npm, yarn, pnpm and bun.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
npm create @phaserjs/game@latest
npx @phaserjs/create-game@latest
yarn create @phaserjs/game
pnpm create @phaserjs/game@latest
bun create @phaserjs/game@latest
```

