TITLE: Creating an Animation in Phaser 3 JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Creates a new animation or returns an existing one if the key is already in use.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.16/CHANGELOG-v3.16.md#2025-04-16_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
const animation = AnimationManager.create(config);
```

