TITLE: Creating a Basic Timeline in Phaser 3.60
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a basic Timeline instance using the Game Object Factory. The Timeline always starts paused and must be explicitly played.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.60/Timeline.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const timeline = this.add.timeline();
```

