TITLE: Configuring Tween Property with Start-From-To Values in Phaser 3
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates setting 'start', 'from', and 'to' values for a tween property. This sets an immediate value, then after delays, it starts tweening from another value to the final value.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.19/CHANGELOG-v3.19.md#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
alpha: { start: 0, from: 0.5, to: 1 }
```

