TITLE: Chaining Sprite Animations in Phaser 3
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to sequence multiple sprite animations to play in order using the new nextAnimsQueue property of the Animation component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.24/CHANGELOG-v3.24.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
this.mole.anims.play('digging').anims.chain('lifting').anims.chain('looking').anims.chain('lowering');
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Using Staggered Tween Delay in Phaser 3
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a staggered tween delay effect using the new StaggerBuilder function. This allows for elements to animate with progressive timing offsets based on their position in a collection.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.19/CHANGELOG-v3.19.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
delay: this.tweens.stagger(500)
```

