TITLE: Setting Scale Manager Snap Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Example of configuring the Scale Manager snap values in the game config to enforce dimension constraints. Useful for pixel-art games or maintaining specific aspect ratios.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.80/CHANGELOG-v3.80.md#2025-04-16_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
{
  snap: {
    width: 16,
    height: 16
  }
}
```

