TITLE: Creating DOM Elements in Phaser 3
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates creation of a DOM Element game object with custom styling and text content. The example shows how to position, size, and style a div element within the Phaser game context.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.17/CHANGELOG-v3.17.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
this.add.dom(x, y, 'div', 'background-color: lime; width: 220px; height: 100px; font: 48px Arial', 'Phaser');
```

