TITLE: Enhanced Animation Control for Particle Emitters in Phaser.js
DESCRIPTION: The 'anims' property in ParticleEmitter configuration now accepts a 'Phaser.Types.Animations.PlayAnimationConfig' object, providing more control over particle animations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.70/CHANGELOG-v3.70.md#2025-04-16_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
new ParticleEmitter({
  anims: {
    // PlayAnimationConfig object
  }
})
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Using Key Events in Phaser 3.16
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the new event emitter functionality of the Key class. This allows direct listening for 'down' and 'up' events on individual keys.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.16/CHANGELOG-v3.16.md#2025-04-16_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const spaceKey = this.input.keyboard.addKey('SPACE');

spaceKey.on('down', () => {
  console.log('Space key pressed');
});

spaceKey.on('up', () => {
  console.log('Space key released');
});
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Vector2 Operations in Phaser 3
DESCRIPTION: New methods for Vector2 manipulation including setting angle and length, normalization, limitation, reflection, mirroring, and rotation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.23/CHANGELOG-v3.23.md#2025-04-16_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
vector.fuzzyEquals(otherVector);
vector.setAngle(angle);
vector.setLength(length);
vector.normalizeLeftHand();
vector.limit(max);
vector.reflect(normal);
vector.mirror(axis);
vector.rotate(angle);
```

