TITLE: Creating Sprites from Tilemap with Extended Properties
DESCRIPTION: Method call to create sprites from tilemap tiles, copying tile properties including rotation, flip states, alpha, visibility and tint to the created sprites.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.80/CHANGELOG-v3.80.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
Tilemap.createFromTiles(fromTile, toTile, spriteConfig)
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Using Nine Slice with Texture Packer Data
DESCRIPTION: Creating Nine Slice Game Objects that automatically use the scale9 data exported from Texture Packer v7.1.0+, eliminating the need to manually specify border sizes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.70/CHANGELOG-v3.70.md#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
CODE:
```
// Create a NineSlice using Texture Packer's scale9 data
const panel = this.add.nineslice(x, y, 'atlas', 'panel');

// Create with explicit size
const panel = this.add.nineslice(x, y, 'atlas', 'panel', 300, 200);

// Override the Texture Packer scale9 data
const panel = this.add.nineslice(x, y, 'atlas', 'panel', 300, 200);
panel.setSlices(10, 10, 10, 10, true); // true skips the scale9 data
```

