TITLE: Configuring Tween Property with From-To Values in Phaser 3
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates setting both 'from' and 'to' values for a tween property. This sets the initial value after delays expire and then tweens to the final value.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.19/CHANGELOG-v3.19.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
