TITLE: Animated Particles with Single Animation
DESCRIPTION: Configuration for particles that play a single animation named 'prism' on emission.
SOURCE: https://github.com/phaserjs/phaser/blob/master/changelog/3.60/ParticleEmitter.md#2025-04-16_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const emitter = this.add.particles(400, 300, 'gems', {
    anim: 'prism'
    ...
});
